<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">

    <style>
        .about {
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .about hr {
            width: 75px;
            height: 6px;
            background: var(--orange);
            border: 1px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 1050px;
            height: 65vh;
            background: var(--orange);
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 20px;
        }


        h2 {
            color: white;
        }

        main p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: wheat;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        a {
            color: #e16d26;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
 
            main{
                margin: 40px 10px;
                padding: 10px;
                height: auto;
            }
        }
    </style>



    <title>Letsbunk</title>
</head>

<body>
    {{>navbar}}
    <center class="about">
        <h1>
            <hr />
            idea-by
        </h1>
    </center>

    <main>
          <section>
            <h2>Welcome to the Idea!</h2>
            <p>
                Hi there! I'm Praveer Ranjan Singh, and I'm excited to share my innovative idea with you. The concept is
                aimed
                at revolutionizing the way students approach mass bunking. Let's explore the idea together!
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>The Concept</h2>
            <p>
                My idea revolves around leveraging technology to optimize the mass bunking experience. From intelligent
                scheduling algorithms to real-time campus maps, the goal is to empower students with the tools they need
                to
                make informed decisions about their attendance.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Meet Praveer Ranjan Singh</h2>
            <p>
                I am passionate about innovation and the potential of technology to enhance our lives. As a student, I
                understand the challenges we face, and this idea is my way of contributing to a more efficient and
                enjoyable
                college experience.
            </p>

        </section>

    </main>

</body>

</html>